southern gulf probably kept at bandar abbas and more such 
missiles in the northern gulf and he fears that china has also 
sold iran ca08 missiles 
the ca08 has a more sophisticated guidance system than the 
silkworm which he described as primitive but carries a 
500pound warhead compared to the 1100pound warhead on the 
silkworm 
