human error and design flaws 
contributed to the collision of two army helicopters that killed 17 
soldiers during night training at fort campbell according to a 
report released today 
human errorpilot error is presumed to be the cause of this 
mishap said the report released at a news conference 
but the report added because the accident was fatal to the 
