and make big drug busts instead of just writing speeding tickets 
he said 
nationwide 8 percent of the nations cocaine seizures in 1987 
were executed during traffic stops and 186 million in cash was 
seized according to the dea 
operation pipeline which began slowly in 198384 has 
forced a nationwide rerouting of drug traffic said gospodarek who 
coordinates the program 
