national laboratory in livermore calif 59 million 
waste pit and silo cleanup at the feed materials production 
center near fernald ohio 40 million 
cleanup of polychlorinated biphenyls at the portsmouth gaseous 
diffusion plant near piketon ohio 38 million 
environmental health and safety actions at the mound plant in 
miamisburg ohio 30 million 
the agency also said major safety and health projects could 
include plantwide fire protection at the savannah river plant 200 
million an upgrade of the ventilation system at the fernald plant 
55 million and an asbestos management program at los alamos 52 
million 
