workers in 1987 and 10 percent more than all government workers 
the american federation of teachers said 
the public is really supporting teachers its the seventh 
straight year salaries have exceeded inflation said f howard 
nelson an assistant research director of the aft which released 
the survey on the eve of its biennial convention 
