that to be too lenient when you steal 25 million of your 
employers money and get a sixmonth sentence what signal does 
that send to the community 
sensi could have received fiveyear prison terms for each of six 
mail fraud counts and 10year sentences for each of the 14 theft 
and interstate transportation of stolen securities counts 
