the italian party which supported stalin in its early days 
it is the lethal combination of the craxi socialist effect 
and the gorbachev effect which has thrown the pci against the 
ropes enzo bettiza a former european parliament deputy from the 
liberal party wrote in the newspaper la stampa of turin 
