<TEXT>
marie lemoin came to the united states with a 
bag full of dreams and a fist full of dollars 
the french woman is part of the wave of foreigners taking 
advantage of the weak dollar to visit america and splurge on goods 
that have become bargains in terms of their own currencies 
ms lemoin 21 arrived in new york this year carrying a 
suitcase a satchel stuffed with guidebooks and slick tourist 
brochures and a wad of travelers checks and assorted us currency 
she said she never expected her money to go so far 
but yvonne gomez and her husband ramiro of sao paulo brazil 
