a machinery repair facility in houston texas and kilngas rampd 
inc which has four employees in its current development phase and 
manages a coal gasification project at east alton ill 
allischalmers said that the plan was conditional among other 
things on the closing of previously announced sales of the 
companys air filter pump and power generation services businesses 
the companys existing common stock holders would receive no 
cash distributions and approximately 206 percent of the 
reorganized companys common stock 
the companys goal is to have the plan consummated by yearend 
1988 bueche said 
